<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Medical Imaging on SiriC's Blog</title><link>https://sirichiu.github.io/tags/medical-imaging/</link><description>Recent content in Medical Imaging on SiriC's Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-tw</language><managingEditor>sirichiu8632@gmail.com (Siri Chiu)</managingEditor><webMaster>sirichiu8632@gmail.com (Siri Chiu)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Sun, 24 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://sirichiu.github.io/tags/medical-imaging/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>高頻超音波微多普勒成像技術在手指肌腱新生血管評估中的應用</title><link>https://sirichiu.github.io/high-frequency-ultrafast-ultrasound-micro-doppler-imaging-for-estimating-finger-tendon-neovascularity-based-on-curvilinear-structure-enhancement/</link><pubDate>Sun, 24 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>sirichiu8632@gmail.com (Siri Chiu)</author><guid>https://sirichiu.github.io/high-frequency-ultrafast-ultrasound-micro-doppler-imaging-for-estimating-finger-tendon-neovascularity-based-on-curvilinear-structure-enhancement/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;我提出一種微血管成像演算法，能夠清楚的看見老鼠腎臟的血管樹狀結構以及手指受傷肌腱的新生血管資訊，最高解析度可達直徑35um。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>射流向量多普勒成像技術在靜脈瓣膜血流分析中的應用</title><link>https://sirichiu.github.io/projectile-vector-doppler-imaging/</link><pubDate>Sat, 23 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>sirichiu8632@gmail.com (Siri Chiu)</author><guid>https://sirichiu.github.io/projectile-vector-doppler-imaging/</guid><description>&lt;script type="text/javascript"
 src="https://cdn.mathjax.org/mathjax/latest/MathJax.js?config=TeX-AMS-MML_HTMLorMML"&gt;
&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;p&gt;動態向量都卜勒(Projectile Vector Doppler Imaging) 比傳統都卜勒影像提供更多樣的血液資訊，如流速、流動，擾流情況等，給予醫師更多診斷資訊。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>手指肌腱位移評估技術</title><link>https://sirichiu.github.io/evaluation-of-hand-tendon-movement/</link><pubDate>Fri, 22 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>sirichiu8632@gmail.com (Siri Chiu)</author><guid>https://sirichiu.github.io/evaluation-of-hand-tendon-movement/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;向量都卜勒成像(Vector Doppler Imaging)能夠觀測更多的目標運動變化，除了應用在血液流速的估算外，也可以應用在肌腱上評估肌腱的滑動性，進而提供肌腱的位移資訊給予醫師更多評估的信息。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>智慧醫療輔助診斷：基於 ResNet50 的胸腔 X 光肺炎分類器</title><link>https://sirichiu.github.io/covid19-chestxray/</link><pubDate>Fri, 22 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>sirichiu8632@gmail.com (Siri Chiu)</author><guid>https://sirichiu.github.io/covid19-chestxray/</guid><description>&lt;script type="text/javascript"
 src="https://cdn.mathjax.org/mathjax/latest/MathJax.js?config=TeX-AMS-MML_HTMLorMML"&gt;
&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;p&gt;本專案旨在開發一套基於深度學習的自動化輔助診斷系統，協助醫療人員快速判讀胸腔 X 光影像 (CXR)。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>